description.excerpt: Trying to use the power of Deep Learning to generate new images, but not willing to invest in hindend GPU? Transfer learning could be a solution.
Note that the FloyHub model is built with Torch (see torch_dcgan.py). To translate this to Keras Torch2Keras.py:
Building a Keras DCGAN using a pre-trained Torch generator

invocation.excerpt: extracts weights as numpy arrays from the first model and feeds them to the second
